    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buddhist saints, the most accomplished of the four types of who have defeated all afflictions and will enter nirvana upon death. Typically depicted as 16 in number, who vowed to remain alive to preserve his teachings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
